s., <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">drive past, overtake</tr_> another, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οἴοισίν μ᾽ἵπποισι παρήλασαν</foreign> ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:638\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">638</biblScope> </bibl> ; but <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">π. Τρηχῖνα</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">drive on</tr_> to Trachis, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0020.tlg003.perseus-grc1:353\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hes.\">Hes.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Sc.\">Sc.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">353</biblScope> </bibl> ; also <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">π. ἐφ᾽ ἅρματος, ἐφ᾽ ἵππου</foreign>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg006.perseus-grc1:1:2:16\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ An.\">An.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.2.16</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg006.perseus-grc1:3:4:46\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.4.46</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n79320.4\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">row</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">sail past</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">παρήλασε νηΐ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:12:186\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">12.186</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"b\" id=\"n79320.5\" level=\"4\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> c. acc. pers., [<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Σειρῆνας] παρήλασαν</foreign> ib. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0